[%#
Variables passed in:

affected_users - Array of user accounts that have demo mode enabled and are distributing their mail to a mail child node.

For more information about how to customize notification templates, read our documentation at https://go.cpanel.net/notificationtemplates

-%]

[%-
    PROCESS "include/colors.tmpl";
    PROCESS "include/styles.tmpl";
    PROCESS 'include/code_block.tmpl';

    WRAPPER 'wrapper/main.html.tmpl';
-%]


<p>
[% CPANEL.locale.maketext("You are receiving this notification because the following accounts have demo mode enabled, and they are distributing their mail to a mail child node:") %]
</p>

<ol>
[% FOREACH user IN NOTICE.affected_users -%]
   <li>[% user -%]</li>
[% END -%]
</ol>

<p>
[% CPANEL.locale.maketext("It is recommended that you remove these accounts as the child node that their mail is distributed to does not have the same demo mode restrictions in place that the parent server has.") %]
</p>

[% END %]
